{"tid":2339306,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"納瓦爾尼設局套料 俄特工爆內褲下毒  克宮斥「妄想被迫害」","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T14:12:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"076f6f12d8c71bac3cf6f417443392bf13701603","tid":2339306,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/KRM2LRITFFBMRIOL4KGQSCE5CE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FKRM2LRITFFBMRIOL4KGQSCE5CE%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt%2B8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=91feba97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201223%2FKRM2LRITFFBMRIOL4KGQSCE5CE%2F&h=8dd6f0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201223/KRM2LRITFFBMRIOL4KGQSCE5CE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼設局套料 俄特工爆內褲下毒 <br />\n克宮斥「妄想被迫害」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qj77-OyWXTwEwis0FjI4wRZObZc=/1000x565/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UKRFQA2RTBBS5NWHS27YTX6DDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQj77-OyWXTwEwis0FjI4wRZObZc%3D%2F1000x565%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUKRFQA2RTBBS5NWHS27YTX6DDM.jpg&h=2a92d9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■納瓦爾尼和嘗試暗殺他的特工通電話。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦爾尼中毒案峯回路轉。他前天公開錄音，指他致電騙倒一名跟蹤他多年的聯邦安全局（FSB）化武特工，套出這次未竟全功的暗殺行動細節，包括原來特工是在他的內褲下毒。FSB否認稱這是揑造抹黑，克里姆林宮更指納瓦爾尼「妄想被迫害」。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼今年8月在西伯利亞飛莫斯科航機上昏迷，在客機緊急降落鄂木斯克後入院急救，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5fcByTK47qeuooMRWA4sDzkFvqs=/1163x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7UFS5FTBPRHVDBC5GTNG35FW5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5fcByTK47qeuooMRWA4sDzkFvqs%3D%2F1163x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7UFS5FTBPRHVDBC5GTNG35FW5U.jpg&h=5473a085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■庫德里亞夫采夫被視為有份參與向納瓦爾尼投毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毀衣滅迹 身體不留毒素<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼前天發表題為「我致電給我的殺手，他供認了」的電話錄音和文字抄本，指他上周在報道公開前數小時，假扮俄羅斯聯邦安全會議秘書帕特魯舍夫的助理，逐一致電報道點名的特工，稱急要問資料寫報告，差不多所有人都掛線，但庫德里亞夫采夫（Konstantin Kudryavtsev）中計，跟他談了49分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n調查報道指庫氏是化武專家，在納瓦爾尼被醫療專機載往柏林後數天，到了鄂。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Gvfcmgx_Zuc7paulnrnQaP13Qnc=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3KNOFLZA7NBOHC2TSEKUGOODLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGvfcmgx_Zuc7paulnrnQaP13Qnc%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3KNOFLZA7NBOHC2TSEKUGOODLE.jpg&h=30911df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■俄聯邦安全局被揭向納瓦爾尼下毒，其總部外前日有納瓦爾尼的支持者示威。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n客機急降救援及時致事敗<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼又問暗殺為何失敗，庫氏指他們沒料到客機會緊急降落，如果沒有跑道上救護車人員迅速施救，「就會完全不同」，又指留意到事件在國際引起軒然大波，「他們都沒料到會這樣」。<br />\n<br />\nFSB稱納瓦爾尼的致電片段是假的，是在外國情報機關支援下有計劃挑釁和抹黑FSB。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HWNOvFNvXUZuhaHNzQzvFwBy6_s=/1103x1932/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EEMXPLRXMJF4XDSFD4CH3VB6NE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHWNOvFNvXUZuhaHNzQzvFwBy6_s%3D%2F1103x1932%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEEMXPLRXMJF4XDSFD4CH3VB6NE.gif&h=10486eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社/路透社"}]}